          "icon": "🎓",
          "title_prefix": "OSCP-TARGET",
          "default_tags": [
            "oscp"
          ],
          "body_lines": [
            "# Target: <TARGET>",
            "",
            "## 🏁 Proofs & Milestones",
            "| Objective | Value / Hash | Screenshot Ref |",
            "|-----------|--------------|----------------|",
            "| local.txt |              |                |",
            "| proof.txt |              |                |",
            "",
            "## 🔍 Phase 1: Enumeration",
            "### 1. Full TCP Discovery (Fast)",
            "```bash",
            "# nmap -p- --min-rate 5000 -v -oN nmap/all-ports <TARGET>",
            "```",
            "",
            "### 2. Service Deep Dive",
            "```bash",
            "# nmap -sC -sV -p <PORTS> -oN nmap/detailed <TARGET>",
            "```",
            "",
            "### 3. UDP Quick Scan",
            "```bash",
            "# nmap -sU -A --top-ports 20 <TARGET>",
            "```",
            "",
            "| Port | Service | Version | Potential Vectors |",
            "|------|---------|---------|-------------------|",
            "|      |         |         |                   |",
            "",
            "## 💥 Phase 2: Initial Access",
            "### Vulnerability Path",
            "- **Name:** ",
            "- **CVE/Link:** ",
            "",
            "### Exploitation Steps",
            "1. [Step 1]",
            "```bash",
            "# Command used to gain shell",
            "```",
            "> **Note:** Attach screenshot of shell with `whoami` and `ipconfig/ifconfig`",
            "",
            "## ⬆️ Phase 3: Privilege Escalation",
            "### Local Enum",
            "- **Finding:** ",
            "- **Vector:** ",
            "",
            "### Escalation Steps",
            "```bash",
            "# Command to escalate",
            "```",
            "",
            "## 🧹 Post-Exploit & Cleanup",
            "- [ ] Deleted exploit scripts",
            "- [ ] Removed uploaded binaries",
            "- [ ] Reverted changes to /etc/hosts",
            "",
            "## 📝 Final Summary for Report",
            "*Quick summary of the attack path for the final write-up.*"
          ]
        },
