          "body_lines": [
            "# Practice Machine: <LABEL> (<IP>)",
            "",
            "## 🎯 Methodology Checkpoints",
            "- [ ] **Service Coverage:** Have I touched every open port at least once?",
            "- [ ] **Default Creds:** Have I tried common defaults for every service?",
            "- [ ] **Source Code:** Did I check for comments/hidden paths in Web?",
