            "| Observation | Hypothesis | Tested? |",
            "|-------------|------------|---------|",
            "|             |            | [ ]     |",
            "",
            "## ⚡ Exploitation & 'The Why'",
            "### How I found it:",
            "",
            "### Why it worked:",
            "```bash",
            "# nmap -p- --min-rate 5000 -v <TARGET>",
            "# masscan -p1-65535 <TARGET> --rate 1000 -e eth0",
            "```",
            "",
            "## 🚧 The 'Stuck' Protocol",
            "> If stuck for >45 mins: Enumerate ALL ports again. Re-read all output files. Look for internal-only ports.",
            "",
            "## 💡 Key Takeaways & Rabbit Holes",
            "### 🐇 Rabbit Holes Encountered",
            "* ",
            "### 🔄 If I did this again...",
            "*What would I check first next time?*",
            "",
